  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The applicant has not submiited sufficient information in the arboricultural report in order to enable assessment of any harm that the protected trees may sustain as a result of the construction of the propsoed 2.43m. high wall which would  form the front and flank boundary of the site contrary to policy CS 13 of the CPS 2011.",
    "Reason : 2 - Insufficent information has been received in order to assess the impact of the proposals on protected species or the local habitat contrary to policy   7.19 of the London Plan 2015, DM 02 of the SPP 2014 & policy CS 13 of the CPS 2011.",
